      <gmd:lineage>
        <gmd:LI_Lineage>
          <gmd:statement>
            <gco:CharacterString>The dataset was created by digitizing in ArcMap the coordinates described in the 2008 edition of the IMO Ships Routeing Guide, documents of the 54th, 55th, 57th, and 58th session of the Sub-Committee on the Safety of Navigation of the IMO, and 3rd session of IMO's Sub-Committee Meeting on the Navigation, Communications, Search and Rescue.

The dataset was further transformed into ETRS89 projections since the original information were based on World Geodetic System 1984 Datum (WGS 84).

This work was carried out in 2017 by Erasmus Mundus MSP trainees Fana Mehari Hagos and Princess Hope Bilgera</gco:CharacterString>
